IMAPAccount lysator
Host imap.lysator.liu.se
User hugo@lysator.liu.se
PassCmd +"pass lysator/mail/hugo"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore lys-local
Path ~/mail/Lysator/
Inbox ~/mail/Lysator/INBOX
AltMap yes
SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore lys-remote
Account lysator

Channel lys
Master :lys-remote:
Slave :lys-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Sync All
SyncState *

# -------------------------------------------------

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User hugo.hornquist@gmail.com
PassCmd +"pass google.com/hugo.hornquist"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/Gmail/
Inbox ~/mail/Gmail/INBOX
AltMap yes
SubFolders Verbatim

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]*
Create Both
Sync All
SyncState *

